buff_desc_durian_ll_master_buff:
Little Legend Master!This unit has become the very best, befriending 6 unique Little Legends!

Now go challenge the Runeterra League and prove your might as Champion!Source: @SourceName@
buff_durian_streaktooltip:
You're on a streak! Keep it up!

Current Streak: @f1@
Current Personal Best: @f2@

Match Hiscore: @f4@
buff_yuumipcompanionshipbuff:
Yuumi has formed a special bond with one of her teammates, enhancing her abilities while Attached to them.

"Meet my new best friend. Time to go on an adventure!"
companion__description_bigknifedog_varia: This dog's not afraid of thunderstorms. They are one.
Half akana, half hound—all on the hunt.
This hound loves tossing the ol' Sun Disc around.
Bringing the Shiba scream to supersonic levels.
companion__description_smolknifedog_vari: Taking sourdough to a new level.
Their soul's desire is…  a nap.
This lil' guy loves pets, just watch out for the static shock!
All dogs go to the spirit world. This dog is no exception.
companion_aoshin_default_description: A descendant of the Storm Dragon lineage, Ao Shin is a guardian of the storm, wielding the duality of gentle rains and the ferocity of lightning and thunder.
companion_bellswayer_lunarrevel2021_desc: Made from the finest porcelain, this ceramic heirloom proudly displays their beautiful craftsmanship for all to regard. If you're lucky enough to win their favor, they brew you a cup of their magical tea.
companion_choncc_default_description: As a whelpling, Choncc is eternally hungry and perpetually sleepy. While favored for their mellow nature, Choncc can be roused to ferocious power if provoked—or cajoled into action with the right snacks.
companion_choncc_lunarbeast_description: Choncc's love of tánghúlu is matched only by his enjoyment of the hologram lion dances that parade the crowded streets of Lunar City during the Festival of Beasts.
companion_choncc_lunarrevel2021_descript: Lunar Revel Choncc is best known for stealing Shisa's ancient recipe for dumplings. Those who can get their hands on one are treated to a wonderful morsel of deliciousness.
companion_description__fenroar_progressd: Hyena Matata. It means be worried.
When Fenroar shoots for the moon, they're certain to blow it up
As if those fangs weren't byte enough.
companion_description__pegasus_progressd: Galloping into the future, one portal at a time.
Let the good times roll. Not too much though, or you'll ruin your econ.
companion_description__qiyanadog_progres: Far out has never been so in.
Progress necessitates breakthroughs in science, technology, and of course, hats.
The futuristic looper with the cuteness.
companion_description_abyssia: Abyssia wields a sword imbued with the power to open rifts between space and time. No one knows what Abyssia looks like, as its true form remains forever hidden beneath its mask.
companion_description_akalidragon: Ossia embodies cool. It commands rhyme and rhythm with an effortless flow that makes even the greatest Little Legends jealous.
companion_description_akalidragon_set7la: Some believe the only true way to communicate with ancient dragons is through dance.
companion_description_aoshin_band1: Ao Shin's songs drag on and on.
companion_description_aoshin_band2: Imagine… a dragon playing rock and roll. Imagine. Dragon.
companion_description_aoshin_band3: The secret to Ao Shin's hair is 50% perm, 50% the power of funk.
companion_description_aoshin_band4: There's nothing daft about this punk.
companion_description_aoshin_poolparty: Summer Splash Ao Shin is here to make waves with their electric (guitar) debut
companion_description_aoshin_promethium_: We should call him “the Star Forger”-- wait a minute…
Ao Shin brings a Harrowing all his own.
You will rune the day you crossed Ao Shin!
He wasn't sleepy, but now he is Awakened.
companion_description_aoshin_spiritfairy: They say that when you're feeling it, the music flows through you. Azure Ao Shin can get behind that.
They say that when you're feeling it, the music flows through you. Azure Ao Shins can get behind that.
Air guitar champion of the Convergence, Galeborn Ao Shin breezes through endless chords, floating cloudy riffs.
Let the savory riffs of this guitarist set your soul ablaze.
The Darkspark Ao Shin creative spark comes from only the darkest skies.
Unlike their other elemental kin, Terra Ao Shin only care to take flight when avoiding steep uphill climbs.
companion_description_balldragon_base_va: Just a tadpole trying to get above water.
Flametongue Poggles defaults to negativity—they're a highly-esteemed critic.
Is it sinking, or is it just efficient diving?
Sugarcone Poggles wants to be the sweetest dragon in all the land! Maybe then, Burno will finally pay attention to them.
companion_description_baron_base: Retiring from their day job in search of a place without Smite.
companion_description_baron_base_variant: Just imagine what the Super Squad Baron buff grants you.
Odyssey Baron has set out on a quest of self-discovery culminating in their arrival in the Convergence.
It's time for Star Guardian Baron to rid themselves of their Epic Monster title in favor of becoming an Epic Hero!
Unable to earn the Mark of the Star Guardian, Star Nemesis Baron devoted themselves to the Guardians' destruction.
The most overwhelming challenger to take to the Convergence.
companion_description_baron_unchartedrea: To make your enemies green with envy.
They're  purple, they're pink, they'll eat you in a blink.
Even Baron needs a vacation sometimes.
companion_description_bat_base: Putting his art school training to good use!
companion_description_bat_v1: This creative critter is a creature of the night.
companion_description_bat_v2: Trouble just rode into town. It's got a mean stare and two big ears.
companion_description_bat_v4: When the Firelights need their hardiest heroes, this little critter takes flight.
companion_description_bat_v5: Ready to make a splash with his larger-than-life artwork!
companion_description_bellswayer_default: A proud, celestial creature found in the Argent Mountains, the Bellswayer's beautiful chiming bells inspire and compel other sprites to attend them. Though they startle easily, Bellswayers are just as quick to resume a composed and regal posture.
companion_description_bigknifedog_base: What game scouts the boards, unaware of death?
companion_description_bigknifedog_varian: Looks like someone got into their owner's Soul Juice stash. It's not for doggie consumption!
companion_description_buglet_sentinel: Flutterbug wants to take over the world -- and eat all the yummiest things in it. But, he's very small. He often has to hide under things in order to not get squashed. While he hides, he machinates on his complex plans.
companion_description_bunny_base: Hoppiness is not a destination, it is a journey.
companion_description_bunny_base_variant: Chubby Choco Bun Bun's ears do not grow back. In other words, do not eat their ears.
From feasting on carrots to feasting on victory… also with carrots.
Red Riding Bun Bun is fearless and—wait, was that Warwick?!
Do they have carrots in space?
I'm not fluffy, I'm yellow and smooth and beautiful!
companion_description_bunny_witchbunbun: Bun Bun's been studying pyromancy for five whole minutes.Witch Bun Bun
companion_description_bunny_witchbunbun_: Bun Bun has the perfect recipe for… carrot cake!
Bun Bun hops the hidden paths and patterns toward victory.
Bun Bun is the hoppiest worker bee in this polli-nation.
They're hopping to be Aurora's familiar.
companion_description_capybara_base_vari: Coffee Kapi's waiting for the caffeine to kick in.
Kapi is a loving caretaker of the spirit springs.
companion_description_chibiaatrox_base: Fury! Chaos! Annihilation! But real small.
companion_description_chibiaatrox_bloodm: Delivering the dark blessing of the Blood Moon.
companion_description_chibiahri_base: Her tails are her good luck charms, and her charm is her foe's bad luck.
companion_description_chibiahri_spiritbl: The Gatekeeper is here to guide you.
companion_description_chibiahri_starguar: She fights for love, justice and cuteness! But mostly cuteness!
companion_description_chibiakali_base: Cold steel, a target, and some ramen are all she needs.
companion_description_chibiakali_kda: 'Kali got a job, 'kali go to work.
companion_description_chibiamumu_base: He's just a little guy… let him give you a hug!
companion_description_chibiamumu_surpris: Surprise! It's your new friend… right?
companion_description_chibiannie_base: The most adorable little girl who's also likely to light you on fire.
companion_description_chibiannie_bluehai: A proud member of the blue-haired girls and… Tibbers.
companion_description_chibiannie_lunarne: Hey, Tibbers—you're looking more cuddly than usual.
companion_description_chibiashe_base: One tribe, one people, one Freljord.
companion_description_chibiashe_dragonma: Weaving magic and flexing on enemies!
companion_description_chibiashe_highnoon: This board ain't big enough for the two of us.
companion_description_chibiblitzcrank_sp: Blitz and Crank are here to groove their way to 1st, or nap their way to 8th.
companion_description_chibibriar_shorkco: Na Na. Na Na. Nananananananana NanaNA!
companion_description_chibicaitlyn_carbs: Get ready! No more playing nice.
companion_description_chibiekko_base: Here for a good time—all the time.
companion_description_chibiekko_fireligh: Top notch inventor by day, leader of the Firelights by night!
companion_description_chibiezreal_base: Looks like some ancient artifact made Ezreal all mini… but he's still got a big head.
companion_description_chibiezreal_battle: Slacking off from class is just preparation for the next adventure!
companion_description_chibiezreal_porcel: Ezreal may be small, but his claws are sharp as ever.
companion_description_chibigwen_base: A doll given life! Only to… shrink back to doll size?
companion_description_chibigwen_cafecuti: Scissors, needles, thread, and little loaves of bread!
companion_description_chibigwen_soulfigh: Kill 'em with kindness! Then stitch 'em up later.
companion_description_chibiirelia_base: Dance like nobody's watching. Fight like your homeland depends on it.
companion_description_chibiirelia_divine: You know what's better than one sacred sword? Many sacred swords!
companion_description_chibiirelia_porcel: A precious li'l protector of porcelain.
companion_description_chibijanna_base: The wind howls a powerful hymn to a graceful goddess.
companion_description_chibijanna_forecas: Cloudy with a chance of convergence!
companion_description_chibijinx_base: All the explosions, with none of the consequences!
companion_description_chibijinx_firecrac: All the explosions, with none of the consequences!
companion_description_chibikaisa_base: Killer instincts with a Chibi attitude.
companion_description_chibikaisa_dragonm: The thing she loves about the Convergence is that it comes in waves.
companion_description_chibikaisa_popstar: She makes that Drum go DUM!
companion_description_chibikaisa_stargua: Kai'Sa and Ina are ready to take down any foe with bunny-powered starlight!
companion_description_chibikatarina_batt: No slacking in battle for this superstar student.
companion_description_chibikayle_aetherw: Ready to purify the galaxy at a moment's notice.
companion_description_chibileesin_base: Live in peace, or rest in pieces
companion_description_chibileesin_dragon: Live in peace, or rest in pieces
companion_description_chibilillia_spirit: An ethereal “Eep!” rings throughout the spirit realm…
companion_description_chibilulu_base: Chibi Lulu and Pix serve up magical tricks!
companion_description_chibilulu_starguar: There's no universe too big to save for Star Guardian Lulu.
companion_description_chibilux_base: The only Chibi who can smile in eighth place.
companion_description_chibilux_porcelain: The only thing that shines more than freshly polished porcelain armor? A blast from Lux's staff.
companion_description_chibilux_starguard: If you want to be worthy of the First Star's call, pigtails are a good place to start.
companion_description_chibimalphite_base: Even a chibi-sized Malphite can shake things up.
companion_description_chibimalphite_mech: Chibi Mecha Malphite is powered up and ready to rock.
companion_description_chibimissfortune_b: Little guns still pack a big punch.
Suit up, hop out, and cover each other's tails.
companion_description_chibimorgana_coven: Tis the Queen of the Coven. The Despoiler of the new world!
companion_description_chibimorgana_immor: Majestically judging your team…are you worthy?
companion_description_chibiorianna_spiri: In Ionia, legend tells of of ball… that got very angry.
companion_description_chibiorianna_t1: T1? More like T100010101 (that's how you say “I won worlds” in binary).
companion_description_chibiriven_base: A broken blade is all she needs to get Top 4.
companion_description_chibiriven_dawnbri: Being the living embodiment of order has its perks. Namely a big, blue sword.
companion_description_chibisett_musicbea: Talk a big game, take a big loss.
companion_description_chibisett_spiritbl: Kanmei get his jab, Akana catch his hook.
companion_description_chibisona_guqin: A string plucked, a soul moved.
companion_description_chibitristana_base: Here comes the boom. The tiniest of booms.
companion_description_chibitristana_drag: Tristana and Riggle are ready to set the stage ablaze!
companion_description_chibivi_base: Trust us, you're not ready for this punchline.
companion_description_chibivi_carbs2: Don't let the size fool you–this brawler still packs a punch!
companion_description_chibiyasuo_base_cl: Running it down with the wind at my back!
companion_description_chibiyasuo_dragonm: Now that he's come to the Dragonlands, will he be able to unite the lost Mirage dragons?
companion_description_chibiyone_base: The grace of a spirit and the edge of a swordsman.
companion_description_chibiyunara_spirit: All those years trapped in the spirit realm gave Yunara plenty of time to practice.
companion_description_chibiyuumi_base: Even a mini-Yuumi causes so much magical mischief!
companion_description_chibiyuumi_bewitch: Every good witch needs an even cuter familiar!
companion_description_chibized_base: It's not your own shadow you should be afraid of.
companion_description_chibizoe_mythmaker: Weaving stories of change through cuteness and chaos.
companion_description_chickeneggtart_bas: Pufflet's soul is warm, their heart is full, and their body is chonky.
companion_description_chickeneggtart_v1: Look at 'em, not a thought between those adorable eyes.
companion_description_chickeneggtart_v5: Pufflet spins and squawks to the groove!
companion_description_chihuahua_base_cla: Stop looking at them like that! That's just their face.
companion_description_chihuahua_base_var: They're ruff, tough, and ready to rumble!
Got their eyes on the World's Championship prize!
companion_description_chip_base: A chip off the ol' block.
companion_description_chip_v2: Is Chip rock or cake? Only one way to find out.
companion_description_chip_v3: That's right. Chip got buff. Red buff.
companion_description_choncc_dragon: Intelligence is knowing when to act, but wisdom is knowing when to nap.
companion_description_choncc_lifeguard: Splash Town locals and tourists alike can feel safer knowing Lifeguard Choncc is on the lookout. On the lookout for the best waves, and Chonccest vibes of course.
companion_description_choncc_poolparty: Splash Town Choncc's dream is winning the Splash Party surfing competition. And with how much napping they do, they're likely to keep on dreaming.
companion_description_choncc_sunkissed: Lifeguard Choncc may be the best swimmer, surfer, and boogie boarder, but Sun Kissed Choncc is better at some really important stuff too. Stuff like, humming, belly bongos, playing the ukulele, and Hula dancing!
companion_description_craggle: Craggle has a soft spot for the vulnerable creatures of the world, and tries to protect them with every ounce of his strength as if he was a giant colossus -- even if he is still growing.
companion_description_creepycat_animetou: Whisker is still hopping universes to find their soul's desire!
Tales of their wrestling prowess have rung through the ages!
Whisker is here to admire their masterpiece.
companion_description_creepycat_base: Whisker just wants what every cat wants: food, a loving home, and total world domination.
companion_description_creepycat_base_var: Even bad felines can change their stripes.
A reformed cat burglar, now a critical member of the Super Squad's Lap Warming Unit.
They're no comedian, but they'll still leave you in stitches.
Star Nemesis Whisker is here to find out what a Star Guardian is made of.
companion_description_creepycat_mythic: First on the list of things to destroy: your favorite sweater. Next: the world.
companion_description_cupcake_variant1: It's Cuppy's party and they'll cry if they want to.
companion_description_cupcake_variant3: Snakes, snails, and puppy dog tails.
companion_description_cupcake_variant4: We all scream into the void for ice cream.
companion_description_cupcake_variant5: A matcha made in the Convergence.
companion_description_doughcat_base: These paws were made for loafin'.
companion_description_doughcat_v1: Doughcat's salmon costume is a bit… fishy.
companion_description_doughcat_v2: Soft and fuzzy on the outside. Delicious on the inside...?
companion_description_doughcat_v3: Honey-roasted ham, perfect for every celebration
companion_description_doughcat_v4: Spoilers: Doughcat has a spicy tuna filling
companion_description_doughcat_v5: Why yes, bread does have a soul.
companion_description_dowsie_base: Looking to add a mystical mer-mage to your party? Look no further than... wait, where'd that Dowsie go? Oh, right—Dowsie can adapt to nearly all surroundings, so you'll have to lure them out. And if you are luring one out, stay calm and remember they're only bashful— until angered, then they might bash-you-full of spells.
companion_description_dowsie_ink: Dowsie loves painting… especially with water colors.
companion_description_dowsie_ink2: Dowsie might be too at peace. She's looking drow-sie out there!
companion_description_dowsie_ink4: That temporary tattoo better be waterproof.
companion_description_dowsie_ink5: Who gave Dowsie a sword? Take that away from her!
companion_description_dowsie_urf: If you're looking for a Dowsie, stay calm and remember they're only bashful— until angered, then they might bash-you-full of spells.
companion_description_dssquid_highnoon: Desperate times in the High Noon Saloon call for a hero, Squinks got the boots and spurs to live up to the test.
companion_description_dssquid_mecha: Justice comes in many forms! For Squink, it's a galactic space suit.
companion_description_dssquid_mecha_vari: This might technically be cannibalism... Whatever. It's delicious!
Call the ink patrol… but not for Edge Lord Squink!
companion_description_dsswordguy_project: They've roamed in pursuit of powerful technology and magic
companion_description_dswhale_koi: This Starmaw gets the Regal treatment at Choncc's Splash Resort.
companion_description_duckbill_base: Duckbill likes to keep their hopes high. That's why they invented the Hopecopter 3000!
companion_description_duckbill_base_vari: Ever the optimist, never a buzzkill.
Pineapple belongs on pizza, no matter what Pizza Time Gloop has to say.
It's their pajama party, and they'll cry if they want to.
Sugarcone Duckbill is always sweet, even when they're in a sour mood.
Here to put a wrench in your plans.
Got a problem? Let Duckbill take a quack at it.
Saving the multiverse, one good deed at a time.
companion_description_duckbill_battleaca: The drip cannot be contained. It's pure ice in their veins.
companion_description_duckbill_battlebun: Duckbill has always wanted to be a cat... Dreams do come true!
companion_description_duckbill_soulfight: What did it cost for Duckbill's soul to awaken? The tears in their eyes say it all.
companion_description_duckbill_starguard: Following the First Star with a pure heart and trusty gadgets!
companion_description_elegantdragon_base: Beautiful, enticing, mesmerizing—and that's just their voice!
This Prancie wants to start their own band, Rage Against the Wings.
Sleek, peaceful, elegant—and more than a little Jaded.
The core tenant of the Darkflight is sacrifice for the greater good.
Their song gives the listeners the chills… and frostbite.
companion_description_elegantdragon_liul: Prance and parade, twirl with all your grace.
The most beautiful part of a lotus pond? Your reflection.
Here's hoping Prancie's vocals only shatter glass, not porcelain.
New year, new fit, new beginnings.
Regality and finesse, only for the best.
companion_description_fairy_default: This mischievous prankster from the spirit realm enjoys playing tricks on hapless mortals who have the misfortune of stumbling upon them. Sweet one moment and deadly the next, Nixie's pranks sometimes take on a life of their own!
companion_description_fairy_set6updateba: Remember to like, comment, and just vibe!
companion_description_featherknight_spir: Darkspark Featherknights power to create life is drawn from the darkest storms.
With a burning passion to paint and create, Ember Featherknights dance with fire.
Galeborn Featherknights power to create life is drawn from the whispering winds.
Terra Featherknights borrow the colors of the earth to paint a better world.
Azure Featherknights power to create life is drawn from the deepest waters.
companion_description_fenroar_base: So, you want the ghost wolf, Fenroar, to join your party. Fenroar are fiercely loyal warriors. But don't let the sword intimidate you. They become eternally bound to their Puproar as well as their friends, which they make quite easily after a round or two of fetch the orbs.
companion_description_fishball_v1: Disco bubble? Spacesuit? Sick dance moves? Blubble's got it all!
companion_description_fishball_v2: Blease be careful of Blubble's sting.
companion_description_fishball_v3: Blubble throws the best summer shindigs.
companion_description_fishball_v4: Blubble drinks in the power of shimmer.
companion_description_fishball_v5: If you want lots of Blubbles, shake some soda!
companion_description_flutterbug: Flutterbug wants to take over the world -- and eat all the yummiest things in it. But, he's very small. He often has to hide under things in order to not get squashed. While he hides, he machinates on his complex plans.
companion_description_gargoyle_sentinel: Craggle has a soft spot for the vulnerable creatures of the world, and tries to protect them with every ounce of his strength as if he was a giant colossus -- even if he is still growing.
companion_description_gemtiger_set4ranke: Victorious Protector was awarded to players who reached Gold or higher in at least one ranked stage of Set 4, Fates. Triumphant Protector was awarded to players who readched Gold or higher all stages of Set 4, Fates.
companion_description_ghosty: The spookiest of the Little Legends.
companion_description_ghosty_dragon_haun: If they breathe fire, how do they blow out the candles on their birthday cake?
The power of the Elder Dragon, and they're using it for pranks…
Ocean Hauntling's favorite pranks end up with someone drenched.
This Hauntling climbs peaks simply to lift their spirits.
Cloudy with a chance of Hauntling.
companion_description_ghosty_galaxiesvic: Triumphant Hauntling was awarded to players who reached Gold or higher in both ranked stages of Set 3, Galaxies. The spookiest galaxies swirled together to form these terrifyingly adorable space wraiths—they roam the vast reaches of the universe searching for golden spatulas and friendship.
companion_description_ghosty_sentinel: The spookiest of the Little Legends.
companion_description_ghosty_victorious: Victorious Hauntling was awarded to players who reached Gold or higher in at least one ranked stage of Set 3, Galaxies. The spookiest galaxies swirled together to form these terrifyingly adorable space wraiths—they roam the vast reaches of the universe searching for golden spatulas and friendship.
companion_description_gloop_base: Gloop's beatboxing skills are unmatched. Wait… those are just snores.
companion_description_gloop_base_variant: Battle? No thanks, Gloop will stick to their hover pillow. Er… literally.
The power to do anything, the motivation to do none of it.
Retired DDR champ, emphasis on the tired.
Stuck in a perpetual sugar crash.
Pop Groove Gloop has the talent to make it big, but none of the drive.
They'll stick anything on their pizza. Anything EXCEPT pineapple.
companion_description_gloop_lunarnewyear: You'd be peachy too if you got this much sleep.
Despite what they say, Shrimpy Gloop is the least shellfish of the Gloop gang.
You can ask for the recipe if you want, but we've never been able to get it quite right.
The type of Gloop you can take home to your grandma's.
They're the gloopiest and they're okay.
companion_description_gloop_musicbeat: Best known for inventing the new music genre, LazyCore.
companion_description_griffin_dragonslay: They may be a Cloud Silverwing, but they'll never rain on your parade.
Don't cross Infernal Silverwing unless you're looking to get roasted—and burnt.
Ocean Silverwing is perplexed by life's mysteries… is it more fun to swim, or fly?
Mountain Silverwing's feathers are so hard they're basically scales.
No one Silverwing should have all that power.
companion_description_grumpylion_stargua: If you chase the stars, you may just end up catching the moon.
You may still like them when they're angry, and they always are.
They might get their stars mixed up sometimes, but their heart's in the right place.
Somehow, Dawnstar Furyhorn always manages to wake up on the wrong side of the bed.
Star Nemesis Furyhorn is here to create chaos in Spatulopolis.
companion_description_hamster_base: To squee, or not to squee? That is the question.
companion_description_hextechbirb_stargu: Tocker's latest project is figuring out how to save the universe AND have time for homework.
companion_description_hundun_base: Their eyes are up here. Somewhere.
companion_description_hundun_base2: Bathing your Hundun in divine springs is vital to Hundun care.
companion_description_hundun_base3: Are those eyes or flowers? Probably both.
companion_description_hundun_base4: Hundun may have twin spirits, but together they make one perfect soul.
companion_description_hundun_base5: Stare into the abyss long enough and it stares back.
companion_description_hundun_base6: Hundun sees all. Hundun is all.
companion_description_hundun_starguardia: When you wish upon a Hun Dun, there's no shortage of fun!
The Star Guardians shall know fluffy, faceless doom.
Hun Dun loves to bask in the early morning light.
Can you face the faceless harbinger of chaos?
companion_description_jawdragon_base_var: Even dragons need a dino onesie.
All this new tech, and they still can't pause the game.
companion_description_jawdragon_mecha: Believe in the Burno who believes in you.
companion_description_jawdragon_mecha_va: "Disco Purgatory" doesn't have the same ring, does it?
Idiot sandwiches never looked so delicious.
Burno was there when the feudal future was the feudal past.
Get in the robot, Burno! We're on the road to victory!
companion_description_kiko_base_classic: Kiko's a friend through thick and thin—though they can be an incurable gossip.
companion_description_kiko_base_variant1: Ready to guide every soul into the Spirit Realm!
companion_description_kiko_base_variant3: It's only a matter of time before the world is shaped to Kiko's grand design!
companion_description_koala_base: Grizzle loves long walks through fragile cities.
companion_description_koala_base_variant: The most likely member of the Super Squad to flame their squadmates.
Star Guardian Grizzle gains their power through frustration with the other Star Guardians.
Barreling across space, fueled by rage without purpose.
After destroying Boogie Wonderland with their galactic foxtrot, Groovy Grizzle has Spatulopolis in their sights
If you can't join them, beat them.
companion_description_kuroshiro_base: Shiro and Kuro are ready for action!
companion_description_kuroshiro_v1: An angel and devil met on the empty plains… and became best friends forever!
companion_description_kuroshiro_v2: Sometimes cats and dogs do get along!
companion_description_kuroshiro_v3: The painted world of Shan Hai Scrolls isn't ready for the precious Shiro and Kuro.
companion_description_kuroshiro_v4: From the darkest star and the brightest light came the bestest of pals.
companion_description_kuroshiro_v5: A mysterious Kanmei and volatile Akana, Shiro and Kuro roam through the realm with boundless energy.
companion_description_leopardgecko_base: Ears up, tongue out, and head empty.
companion_description_leopardgecko_class: What it lacks in hastiness, it makes up for in tastiness.
Poptail's tongue has tasted every flavor in the known multiverse. Delish!
I'm getting a sugar crash just looking at them.
companion_description_miner_rpg: No longer hiding in the ground, Molediver joined the Fellowship to put their melee skills to the test.
companion_description_minion_variant3: This hot rod only plays heavy metal on their stereo. K/DA who?
companion_description_minion_variant5: Beep beep! This sweet lil friend brings tricks and treats!
companion_description_moth_variant2: Do they make honey or moth balls? Maybe both?
companion_description_moth_variant3: Emerging from their cocoon, just in time for winter.
companion_description_nimblefoot_base: A cunning master of speed, traps, and thievery, Nimblefoot quickly turns any journey into a mischievous misadventure. Their enchanted red pouch can hold anything and everything, from gold to orbs to… wait, is that cheese?
companion_description_nimblefoot_set8bat: Cunning, conniving, and down right crooked.
companion_description_owl_base: Justice never sleeps! At least… not at night.
companion_description_owl_base_variant2: Birds of a feather fight crime together!
companion_description_owl_base_variant4: Charm is a weapon not to be underestimated.
companion_description_owl_base_variant5: Super Noctero's got a nose for crime, small rodents, and the occasional lizard.
companion_description_pegasus_default: The embodiment of wispy firelight, the Lightcharger can be seen soaring across the skies of Targon as dusk turns to night. It bathes in the moon's most radiant glow, galloping nobly from east to west and protecting the world from the eternal darkness.
companion_description_pegasus_ink: Galloping straight off the scroll and onto the carousel!
companion_description_pegasus_ink2: Lightcharger is so fast, most can't see them coming. The bells help with that.
companion_description_pegasus_ink3: Tattoo magic is dangerous… but it sure does make a statement.
companion_description_pegasus_ink4: The spirit realm doesn't need protection. Still… Lightcharger spruces up the place.
companion_description_pegasus_ink5: Not sure which is more pointy: their glowing horn or magical, floating swords. Either way, stay clear.
companion_description_pegasus_lightcharg: Built from horsepower and star power.
companion_description_pegasus_progressda: More horsepower than you can handle.
When science goes too far, Lightcharger gets there faster.
companion_description_penguknight_birthd: So cute and forever full of questions
companion_description_penguknight_dragon: What started with a fun dragon cosplay ended up with parental responsibilities…
companion_description_penguknight_esport: Esports Pengu has the most consistent top eight performances throughout the multiverse.
companion_description_penguknight_order: In great times of need Order Pengu can be summoned. On the Convergence, times of need happen all too frequently.
companion_description_penguknight_set5la: When Pengu made contact with the corrupting forces of the Black Mist, Chaos Pengu burst from the Feather Knight we know and love. And—while Chaos Pengu's hair, dance moves, and rap theme are superior—it's important to note that Chaos Pengu is just that, superior.
companion_description_penguknight_spirit: Darkspark Featherknights know the power to create life is drawn from the darkest storms.
With a burning passion to paint and create, Ember Featherknights know how to dance with fire.
Galeborn Featherknights know the power to create life is drawn from the whispering winds.
Terra Featherknights borrow the colors of the earth to paint a better world.
Azure Featherknights know the power to create life is drawn from the deepest waters.
companion_description_piximander_base: Piximander's beauty routine costs an arm and a leg. But don't worry—they regenerate.
companion_description_piximander_base_va: Buzzing with affection, stinging with rejection.
When you're the last of your kind, you stop being kind.
Loves long crawls in caves and edible flowers. Dislikes sinister plots and fake friends.
Fruity, tooty, and just as snooty.
The pursuit of knowledge demands you ax-o-lotl questions.
The only one who's “endangered” here is you.
What's black, white, and stealing your carousel items?
companion_description_piximander_rio1: From out of the Sump, looking for salvation.
companion_description_piximander_rio2: Rio is ready to rebel and rock out!
companion_description_piximander_rio3: The Firelights love when Rio runs around the hideout.
companion_description_piximander_rio4: Corrupted, yet still oh so cute.
companion_description_poro_cosplay2: Poro brought their best cosplay to the hangout.
companion_description_poro_cosplay3: Always on the lookout for honey-flavored Poro snax!
companion_description_poro_cosplay4: Poro makes sure that Yone is Unforgotten.
companion_description_poro_cosplay5: Poro comes bearing gifts… easy LP!
companion_description_poro_variant1: Guiding a sledding adventure through a harsh blizzard? Nose-problem.
companion_description_poro_variant2: Destroyer of worlds and devourer of Poro-Snax.
companion_description_poro_variant3: A skilled blacksmith of fire and fluff.
companion_description_poro_variant4: The bravest of Poros, shining in Demacian steel.
companion_description_poro_variant5: Those waffle-horns are freshly-dipped. And just look at that form!
companion_description_porofluft_base: So soft, so squishy, so... deadly...
companion_description_powdermonkey_base_: Powder Monkey's got some punch to 'em!
Does Powder Monkey love a good Snow Day?
This Powder Monkey's creations always manage to go out with a bang!
The best part of their soul awakening? Infinite explosives!
companion_description_pupdragon_base: Bungo has no pause button—but they do have four paws!
companion_description_pupdragon_base_var: A Bungo by any other name.
Calm, composed, tranquil—who are we kidding they're still a Bungo!
No matter how many times you say it, they'll still be chasing the stars.
Found chasing their tail and big vertical traits.
companion_description_qiyanadog: QiQi's hobbies include looking good and turning heads. Whether it's music, fashion or battling fierce enemies, QiQi always takes center stage.
companion_description_qiyanadog_progress: Their stage name is QiQi Stardust, their performances… Electric.
companion_description_razorbeak_base: They can walk the walk, but can they squawk the squawk?
companion_description_razorbeak_variant1: No, this raptor family possesses no hoops or circles of the fruity variety.
companion_description_razorbeak_variant2: If you aren't crying from spice overload, are you even truly living?
companion_description_razorbeak_variant3: Which came first, the bird or the fish?
companion_description_razorbeak_variant4: Not sure the Sun-Disc worked as intended.
companion_description_razorbeak_variant5: Crow or raven? Would it kill you to find out?
companion_description_scratch_base: Scratch's music is so underground it isn't even on ConvergeCloud.
companion_description_scuttlecrab_base: Want to destroy this city? You'll have to go through Scuttle's rigid external skeleton first!
companion_description_scuttlecrab_base_v: Looking fresh, even in saltwater environments.
No one can outrun the long arm of the claw.
Star Nemesis Scuttle is always in a crabby mood.
companion_description_seaangel_variant1: Harsh vibes can't touch this gliding groover.
companion_description_seaangel_variant2: Sweet treats and even sweeter attire!
companion_description_seaangel_variant4: The cutest, most luminous star to ever be consumed.
companion_description_seaangel_variant5: The Crimson Circle has an adorable, bloodthirsty mascot.
companion_description_sennabunny: Melisma stays true to the beat. No matter the occasion, it stands ready to drop the hottest track you never knew you wanted.
companion_description_sennabunny_lunarne: For the ones that dance life into reality, who see beauty in the purity of the natural, this one is for you.
Puts the fire into spitting fire.
Only someone as kind as Heavenly Jade Melisma would think to invite a party pooper to sing a duet.
Lucky Rabbit Melisma considers themselves a trendsetter, but lately they've been taking style inspo from Bun Bun.
companion_description_sgcat: Dango is the hungriest of all the Little Legends.
companion_description_sgcat_superhero_ra: Is it possible to be TOO on time?
Everyone knows round is the most aerodynamic shape.
Rolling through life with rose-colored goggles.
companion_description_sgpig: Fuwa longs to someday find the Guardian it's destined for.
companion_description_sgpig_rpg: No dungeon or path is too treacherous when you have a healer like Fuwa on your side!
companion_description_sgshisa: Shisa aims to protect the Star Guardians and all those in its care
companion_description_sgshisa_mecha: Pilot outfit? Check. Mindmeld tail to sync with their mech? Check. An entire mech's worth of hairspray? Double check.
companion_description_sgshisa_mecha_vari: To defeat evil, one must become the supreme evil.
The groove isn't a sound—there's no sound in space.
Where'd Shisa get their mech-pilot's license? A cereal box?
Ooh… That's why Shisa's hair is so humongous. It's full of secret recipes!
companion_description_shark_base: Just gotta keep swimming. Y'know… or else.
companion_description_shark_base_variant: They're in the business of violence.
Shoot for the moon, and land upon the shores.
Eyes black as the night sky.
companion_description_smolknifedog_base: Pet the pupper… at your own peril.
companion_description_smolknifedog_proje: Knife Pup is here to take a chainsaw to [your/your enemy's] code.
The cutest pup throughout space AND time
Final City's most pointy defender. Also its smallest.
Built out of the cutest scraps the Creator could find.
Go forth, Knife Pup, there's a galaxy that needs defending!
companion_description_snake_base: No sudden moves, or Snek might strike!
companion_description_snake_lantern: This little Snek hopes to be a huge beast one day, worthy of the Dragon Lantern!
companion_description_snake_mushroom: Snek's favorite food is the mushiest of mushrooms!
companion_description_snake_starguardian: And whossse Star Guardian familiar is thisss?
companion_description_spiritfox_starguar: Chasing stars while dusting off the ol' running tails.
Ever since they met Chibi Ahri, accusations of who stole whose style have been tearing the Convergence apart.
Cloud Catcher Hushtail can't seem to keep their head out of the clouds.
Lovely Guardian Hushtail started their own League of protectors with a membership capacity of one.
A powerful ally of the Star Nemesis— not out of nefarious intentions, just spite of others' delight.
companion_description_squink: Sometimes Squink gets so scared that it inks itself, and in its frantic attempt to dash away it accidentally blots out an entire galaxy!
companion_description_starmaw: Starmaw swims leisurely through the galaxies, oblivious to all other life around it. It's known as a devourer of worlds, but really it just happens to swallow a planet or two while it's yawning.
companion_description_styletwogaren_godk: It is he who guards against all evil, he who stands as a bastion of Order.
companion_description_styletwojhin_darkc: There is a certain elegance in annihilation.
companion_description_styletwosenna_high: The only thing she loves more than cute tacticians...  horses!
companion_description_styletwothresh_hig: Frontier's full of lost souls—and Thresh is aiming to collect.
companion_description_styletwovayne_proj: PROJECT's code will break with her relentless hunt.
companion_description_styletwowarwick_ba: Fear the beast who's broken his chains.
companion_description_styletwowarwick_ca: Touched by shimmer. Blessed by the Arcane.
companion_description_styletwoyasuo_nigh: Order and chaos both thrive within his sword.
companion_description_tftavatar_bubblete: Full of flavor. Full of friendship!
companion_description_tftavatar_evil: They're actually a super good Sprite…super good at being evil.
companion_description_tftavatar_healthpo: Don't drink it just because it's adorable!!
companion_description_tftavatar_hotsprin: Sauna Sprite is just too…Tired. To. Use. Completed. Sentences.
companion_description_tftavatar_order: It's a heavy burden being the Sprite responsible for Order. Good thing Sprites are featherlight.
companion_description_tftavatar_set11upd: Let's build a happy little cloud. And… done!
companion_description_tftavatar_set5laun: Chaos Sprite has never understood River Sprite. But we're sure they'd be friends if flames weren't so easily extinguished by water.
companion_description_tftavatar_set6laun: The power to change everything, the Sprite to do nothing.
companion_description_tftavatar_set6upda: The type of Sprite you can take home to meet your houseplants.
companion_description_tftavatar_superfan: Sprite knows every fan chant and all of the choreo.
companion_description_tftavatar_superher: As super as a Sprite could ever hope to be!
companion_description_tocker: Tocker is constantly tinkering with things to make them better, even on his own body!
companion_description_turtle_spiritfairy: Let the gentle waves of sleep wash over you, and carry you to new shores.
Let the gentle waves of sleep wash over you, and carry you to new shores.
Slow and steady wins the race,  just like Terra Paddlemar, and the moving tectonic plates.
The Ember Paddlemars' scroll that takes ages to ink takes only seconds to burn.
Hold fast your brush, for Darkspark Paddlemars will guide you through even the stormiest seas.
Galeborn Paddlemars best ideas come and go with the breeze.
companion_description_umbra_poolparty2: Lifeguard Umbra balances their music career with their passion for saving swimmers.
companion_description_umbra_poolparty3: A passionate mixologist with a flair for blending trait combos with emote wombos.
companion_description_umbra_poolparty4: Sunkissed Umbra likes everything but sand. It's coarse and rough and irritating, and it gets everywhere.
companion_description_umbra_rpg: Umbra's joining in on the adventure to protect what's theirs, whether that's their loot, their lute, or their friends!
companion_description_umbraband1: Slowburn Umbra plays for late-game comebacks.
companion_description_umbraband2: Watch out, this metal is HOT!
companion_description_umbraband3: Umbra likes flying high. It makes their beat drops all the more legendary.
companion_description_umbraband4: Umbra's flames are as dark as their heart.
companion_description_umbraband5: Who needs a mirror ball when you're this shiny?
companion_description_voideye_base: Can you pet the Khat'Sai? Yes. Should you? Also yes.
companion_description_voideye_variant1: Terror of the deep—and of your enemies.
companion_description_voideye_variant2: Returned from stone, and ready to protecc!
companion_description_voideye_variant3: You scream, eye scream, we all scream for... ice cream?
companion_description_voideye_variant4: Legends say the Khat'Sai constellation chases their own tail in an endless game.
companion_dssquid_kda1_description: Channeling Evelynn's dramatic edge has this Squink feeling its ALL OUT fantasy.
companion_dssquid_kda2_description: Evelynn's fierce energy has galvanized this easily-frightened Squink to adopt her look in hopes it can gain some of her confidence.
companion_grumpylion_kda1_description: Kai'Sa's new look inspires this Furyhorn to show off not only its strength but its style.
companion_grumpylion_kda2_description: This quiet Furyhorn loves Kai'Sa's precise and expressive dance moves and hopes it can be as polished as she is one day.
companion_grumpylion_lunarbeast_descript: A beast on the dance floor, this Furyhorn's moves are some of the best in Lunar City. Unfortunately for the guests around them, tearing up the floor means tearing up the floor... literally.
companion_grumpylion_lunarrevel2021_desc: People think this little Furyhorn is a menace, but they're just misunderstood. All they want is to join in on the festivities and celebrate the New Year, but they're scared off by firecrackers and bright red lanterns.
companion_name_chibileesin_dragonfist1: Prestige Chibi Dragon Fist Lee Sin
companion_pegasus_kda1_description: From Seraphine's long beautiful mane to her moving music, this Lightcharger loves everything about the newest K/DA collaborator. But as it defends the world from eternal darkness, it appreciates Seraphine's unwavering optimism most of all.
companion_pegasus_kda2_description: This Lightcharger has always dreamed about what Seraphine would have looked like if she was in POP/STARS—so it turned its dream into reality!
companion_penguknight_kda1_description: This Knight's newly inspired by Akali's fresh beats, and is determined to bring her energy to its performance. Even if its choreography is slightly more waddley.
companion_penguknight_kda2_description: Akali's fierce originality has captivated this Little Legend. Now that it's snagged its idol's signature hat, nothing can stand in the way of its dream: to be the first Featherknight to shine onstage for an audience.
companion_sgpig_default_description: Fuwa longs to someday find the Guardian it's destined for.
companion_sgshisa_lunarbeast_description: The slickest magical monkey around, Shisa is only afraid of one thing: a bad hair day.
companion_sgshisa_lunarrevel_description: Shisa's been a part of the Lunar New Year celebration longer than anyone can remember. Part trickster, part warrior, this little monkey king is the cleverest of the bunch!
companion_spiritfox_kda1_description: This Hushtail will follow Ahri in whatever form she takes on. Glowing with the group's recent success, it's ready to slay.
companion_spiritfox_kda2_description: This Hushtail feels a special kinship with Ahri, and has morphed itself into the colors of her iconic POP/STARS outfit. Its dream is to follow K/DA around on tour.
companion_tft_avatar_lunarrevel2021_desc: Filled with savory pork and flavorful shrimp, this little Dumpling Sprite is sure to be at your table this New Year. Wait, you thought they're for eating? No! Are you insane?
companion_umbra_default_description: Umbra, a shadow dragon, appears guarded and reserved at first. However, once a mortal has earned their trust, they show sweet affection and fierce dedication, conjuring shadow and flame to defend their allies.
